quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,40,"Habeenka in ka mid ahna ku tasbiixso Ammaanahiisa iyo salaadaha ka dambow."
  50,41,"Dhageyso Maalinka markuu dhawaaquhu ka dhawaaqi meel dhow."
  50,42,"Maalinka ay maqli qaylo Xaq ah, kaasu waa Maalinka soo bixinta (Qiyaame)."
  51,34,"Looga soo calaameeyey xagga Rabbigaa xadgudbayaasha{2}."
  51,35,"Markaasaan ka soo bixinnay halkaa wixii ku jiray ee mu’miniin ah."
  51,36,"Kamase aanu helin gudaheeda (magaaladaa) wax aan aheyn hal guri oo muslimiin ah{2}."
  52,25,"Qaarkood (ehlu Jannaha) waxay qaabili qaar kale iyagoo is-wareysan."
  52,26,"Waxay odhan: Waxaan ka hor (intaan adduunka joognay)ahayn kuwo ehelkayaga dhexdooda ka cabsada(cadaabka Ilaahay)."
  52,27,"Markaasuu Alle nagu manneystay (denbi dhaaf) oo naga dhowray cadaabka hanfiga kulul."
  53,19,"Ee (gaaloy) ka warrama (sanamyada) Al-Laat iyo Al-Cuzza."
  53,20,"Iyo Manaat, tan seddexaad ee kale{2}?"
  53,21,"idinku ma waxaad leedihiin labka Isaguna dheddigga?"
  54,10,"Markaasuu baryey Rabbigi (isagoo leh): Waa la iga adkaadaye ii soo hiilli."
  54,11,"Markaasaan ka soo furnay albaabadii daruuraha biyo da’aya oo badan."
  54,12,"Kana soo burqinnay dhulka ilo (biyo ah). markaasay biyihii (cirka iyo dhulka) is qabteen oo ku kulmeen arrin la qaddaray ."
  55,4,"Oo baray caddeynta (hadalka iyo waxa uu dooni)."
  55,5,"Qorraxda iyo dayaxu waxay ku socdaan xisaab."
  55,6,"Xiddigaha iyo geedahuna way sujuudaan (Alle dartiis){2}."